       crl2pkcs7 - Create a PKCS#7 structure from a CRL and
       certificates.

SSYYNNOOPPSSIISS
       ooppeennssssll ppkkccss77 [--iinnffoorrmm PPEEMM||DDEERR] [--oouuttffoorrmm PPEEMM||DDEERR] [--iinn
